MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 987

EXCLUDING FROM THE OPERATION OF PROCLAMATION NO. 330, DATED NOVEMBER 27, 1964, WHICH RESERVED FOR THE USE AND ADMINISTRATION OF THE VETERANS FEDERATION OF THE PHILIPPINES A CERTAIN PARCEL OF THE PRIVATE DOMAIN OF THE GOVERNMENT LOCATED IN THE CITY OF DAVAO, ISLAND OF MINDANAO, CERTAIN PORTIONS OF THE LAND EMBRACED THEREIN, AND DECLARING THE SAME OPEN FOR DISPOSITION TO THE ACTUAL AND BONA FIDE OCCUPANTS THEREOF UNDER THE PROVISIONS OF ACT 3038 AND REPUBLIC ACT NO. 477, AS AMENDED

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, FIDEL V. RAMOS, President of the Philippines, do hereby exclude from the operation of Proclamation No. 330, dated November 27, 1964, which reserved for the use and administration of the Veterans Federation of the Philippines a certain parcel of land of the private domain of the government located in the City of Davao, Island of Mindanao, certain portions of the land embraced therein, and declaring the same open for disposition to actual and bona fide occupants thereof under the provisions of Act 3038 and Republic Act No. 477, as amended, subject to future survey, which portions are more particularly described as follows:

LOT I of Consolidation subdivision plan of Lot A-2-A-2-B-2-B-1, Psd-17184 and Lot 6-B-2-C-3-A, Psd-6416.

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot 1, of the consolidation and subdivision PLAN of Lot A-2-A-2-B-2-B-1, Psd-17184 and Lot 6-B-2-C-3-A, Psd-6416, situated in the City of Davao, Island of Mindanao. Bounded on the East points 1 to 4 by Lot 2, consolidation and subdivision plan of Lot A-2-A-2-B-2-B-1, Psd-17184 and Lot 6-B-2-C-3-A, Psd-6416 on the South points 4 to 5 by Monteverde Street; on the west points 5 to 6 by Lot A-2-A-2-B-2-C-2-B-12-C-1, Psd-1187; and on the N., points 6-1 by LOT A-2-A-2-B-2-C-2-B-12-C-1, Psd-11987. Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan, Being N 40 deg. 29’W., 173.31 m. from mon. No. 5, Davao Townsite, Davao City, thence;

7.50 m. to point 2;

4.00 m. to point 3;

18.66 m. to point 4;

13.80 m. to point 5;

25.60 m. to point 6;

9.60 m. to point of

beginning, containing an area of THREE HUNDRED TWENTY-FOUR (324) SQUARE METERS, more or less.

LOT 3 of Consolidation subdivision Plan of Lot A-2-A-2-B-2-B-1, Psd-17184 and Lot 6-B-2-C-3-A, Psd-6416

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot 3 of the Consolidation and subdivision plan of Lot A-2-A-2-B-2-B-1, Psd-17184 and Lot 6-B-2-C-3-A, Psd-6416, situated in the City of Davao, Island of Mindanao. Bounded on the North points 1 to 2 by Lot 6-B-2-B-2-C-3-B, Psd-6414; on the Northeast points 2 to 4 by Lot 6-B-2-B-2-B, Psd-4197; on the East points 4 to 5 by Lot A-2-A-2-B-2-c-1, Psd-6416; on the South points 5 to 6 by Monteverde Street; and on the West points 6 to 8 and 8-1 by Lot 2, consolidation subdivision plan of Lot A-2-A-2-B-2-B-1, Psd-1784 and Lot 6-B-2-C-3-A, Psd-6416.

Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan being N., 32 deg. 05’W., 158.56 from Mon. No. 5, Davao Townsite, Davao City; thence;

